                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4434" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0699</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9222 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">回力：老字号品牌的激活之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WARRIOR: On the Way of Old Brand Activation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘勇，陈秀林，杨文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈涛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海回力鞋业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">回力；品牌定位；品牌激活；整合营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Warrior; Brand Positioning; Brand Activation; Integrated Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">回力于1927年创建，1956年归为国有化，在物质匮乏的时代供不应求，深受追捧。但是由于经济环境的变化，来自国内外市场竞争日益激烈，回力于2000年前后破产。紧接着，回力进行了破产重组，经历了一系列的阵痛和磨难，抓住难得的机遇，通过三次转型整改走上了漫漫品牌激活之路。首先是转变其经营理念和思维模式，发现品牌存在的问题；然后进行品牌剖析、品牌找位、品牌再定位；同时应用整合营销传播策略，扩展品牌知名度，改善品牌联想，与消费者产生情感共鸣，进而共创价值；并对产品和渠道经营模式进行创新，采用网络直销平台扩大销量，最终使回力这个民族老品牌重新焕发活力。本案例描述了回力公司破产后的重整、转型、创新、激活之路，旨在分析回力老品牌的激活经验，为其他民族品牌的振兴与发展提供启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">WARRIOR company was founded in 1927 and nationalized in 1956. Before Chinese economic reform，it was one of the most popular shoe brands in China. Due to the change of economic environment around 2000, it was unable to cope with the fierce market competition at home and abroad, and went bankrupt eventually. 
Through a series of tough times, Warrior began to bankruptcy reorganize and walk in the brand activation road. By grasping the rare opportunity, it warrior re-examine brand positioning, carry out three transformations. Firstly Warrior changed its marketing concepts and thinking model, found its brand problems; and then performed brand re-analyzing, locating, positioning; in the meanwhile applied integrated marketing communication strategy, expanded brand awareness, improved brand association and created brand value with consumers; what’s more, it carried out product and marketing channel innovation, taking the online platform into considerations to enlarge the sales. Ultimately, warrior is once again popular in the world. 
This case described the transformation, innovation and activation of Warrior shoes after bankruptcy. The purpose is to analyze the successful experience of Warrior and hope to bring enlightenment to revitalization of other old brands in China.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">理解品牌管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
                            </tr>
